  "image": "6594\\6594.jpg",
  "title": "4-Way Stretch",
  "description": "Lost in grief, a drag king finds himself stretched by the four components of time; past, present, future and... gender identity. In Stretcher Hartout’s second one man show and first time fringe debut, this drag king rekindles himself with his femininity and labours to fit in non-toxic masculinity.",
  "credits": "<strong>Playwright</strong>: Stretcher Hartout<br/><strong>Director</strong>: Stretcher Hartout<br/><strong>Cast</strong>: Stretcher Hartout<br/><strong>Stage Manager</strong>: Abyss<br/>",
  "website": "https://www.instagram.com/stretcherforever",
  "plain_language": "4-Way Stretch is a personal narrative of Stretcher Hartout navigating the discovery of his gender identity through the queer artform of drag. Relating to his own experiences, Stretcher unpacks the complicated and underrepresented history of drag kings in the media. Through drag acts and storytelling, does Stretcher find an answer to his struggles? Or is he left questioning his discoveries?",
